        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center">
          <a href={registerUrl} class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-blue px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-white shadow-lg shadow-blue-200 transition hover:bg-brand-blue-dark">
            Crear mi aula gratis →
